At last! We've completed our extensive survey of the best new ideas in asset management and now you can read about all the great ways next-generation funds are bending the efficient frontier in your clients' favor. Get serious: they don't need you to put them on a random walk. They pay you for something better, and odds are good someone in this book has the keys to that enhanced experience.






  Read More >   <https://news.tamps.com/NjY2LVBIQS05NTgAAAGZQVnZhqcRo_d8zmhbRe6W_cQ9BJH9YppBC30JLcs9p67tKnf37lIsu6mAbLbkYu4pS7ywMs8=>











































