“HIVE is in the data center business,” Holmes emphasizes, pointing to the core infrastructure that drives the company’sunique value. “The key factors for this production are, you need data centers, and you need power.”






  Read More >   <https://news.tamps.com/NjY2LVBIQS05NTgAAAGZQVnZhiNPGVex7o8UdLCq8AuuLruq1f3X5tPxtXPOcCyOMovY40U7HeEjWZkuUoPdN8avbvQ=>











































