El-Erian: Trump's Economic Goals May Prove 'Too Difficult' If GDP Growth Falls Below 1% <https://news.tamps.com/NjY2LVBIQS05NTgAAAGZQVnZhi0d3yIOPfItAB4A12DJxdxDHExciuAwC7VKgvZQ9BJiuFNcWUsuUdcy_mhmwXSPQb4=>







“We’re getting closer to stall speed,” El-Erian said. “And if we get to stall speed, then the journey becomes too difficult for the destination. And that’s going to be the big question as we look forward.”






  Read More >   <https://news.tamps.com/NjY2LVBIQS05NTgAAAGZQVnZhi0d3yIOPfItAB4A12DJxdxDHExciuAwC7VKgvZQ9BJiuFNcWUsuUdcy_mhmwXSPQb4=>











































